title: Theatricality vs. Dishonesty (Ask Yourself, Durianrider, Vegan Gains, Cory & Tara McCarthy)
description: This is not a new video but, to my astonishment, this is still a new issue: the commentary on Durianrider is still very salient today, and, even more strangely, on the connection between Ask Yourself (and Vegan Gains) and the overt racism of Tara & Cory McCarthy.
